{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, and then I found out that they didn't take away all of them, because some were hiding.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some weren't-- I mean, as many as they could, they gathered and they took them on the trains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I found out that my, my father and mother were taken.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My aunts, and uncles, and cousins the same age as I was, they were there too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were, in the beginning, in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But then they came to Hanaczow, and then they were, you know, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they took them away, but my father managed-- and I don't know how it happened, but he jumped the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was the one who came back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one of my father's brothers, the, the half-brother, also came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "His family, his children, everybody was gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then they came back to the ghetto, which were much less than they started out with, maybe half or whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then they stayed, again, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The same thing-- fear, and they didn't know what the next day's going to bring.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This woman, I found out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then also, they took some-- they needed some of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had, like, a Judenrate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that they need some Jewish people to, to-- when they needed something, you know, the Germans, they, they would have-- it, it was like a little-- what would you say?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Judenrate-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, how can I explain?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, like a little Jewish authority that they can come, and they can, you know, whatever they needed-- they needed money, they needed jewelry, they needed whatever, that the Germans have somebody to come to.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
